{"tid":2134624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港府DQ參選人押後立會選舉 德國將暫停與香港引渡協議","createTime":"2020-08-01T00:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T01:00:38.000Z","uid":219379,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a66257c478779cf01a1e783417c39db6836f4bb","tid":2134624,"uid":219379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T00:31:18.000Z","msg":"德國外長馬斯（Heiko Maas）周五（7月31日）宣布，將暫停與香港之間的引渡協議，理由是香港政府押後立法會選舉1年，但未有提及實施的具體時間。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯表示，港府取消12名反對派人士參選資格及押後選舉，再次侵犯香港市民的權利；德國已多次表明，期望中國在國際法的框架下承擔其法律責任，包括保障《基本法》賦予港人的權利及自由公平的選舉。<br />\n<br />\n除德國外，加拿大、澳洲、英國及新西蘭本月先後暫停與香港之間的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n已宣布跟香港暫停引渡協議的國家（宣布日期）︰<br />\n加拿大（7月3日）<br />\n澳洲（7月9日）<br />\n英國（7月20日）<br />\n新西蘭（7月28日）<br />\n德國（7月31日）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9Cdq%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-000445432.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259Cdq%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0-000445432.html&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=9ac4588c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9Cdq%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-000445432.html</a>"},{"pid":"18a466c80a232606c521522634c73711d7e18201","tid":2134624,"uid":219379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"港府正式成為逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/